SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Grade], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDataExported], [t].[StartDate], [t].[TimeSlot], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CourseId], [t0].[ProcessedAt], [t0].[RejectionReason], [t0].[RequestedAt], [t0].[Status], [t0].[StudentId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedAt], [t0].[Email], [t0].[FullName], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[LastLoginAt], [t0].[PasswordHash], [t0].[Role]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[EndDate], [c].[Grade], [c].[IsActive], [c].[IsDataExported], [c].[StartDate], [c].[TimeSlot]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[Id] = @__courseId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CourseId], [c0].[ProcessedAt], [c0].[RejectionReason], [c0].[RequestedAt], [c0].[Status], [c0].[StudentId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FullName], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LastLoginAt], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[Role]
    FROM [CourseRegistrations] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [c0].[StudentId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CourseId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CourseId], [c0].[ProcessedAt], [c0].[RejectionReason], [c0].[RequestedAt], [c0].[Status], [c0].[StudentId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FullName], [u].[Grade], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LastLoginAt], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[Role]
    FROM [CourseRegistrations] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [c0].[StudentId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CourseId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]

) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CourseId]

    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [CourseRegistrations] AS [c0]
    WHERE [c].[Id] = [c0].[CourseId] AND [c0].[Status] = 2) AS [StudentCount], [c].[IsActive], CASE

    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[Id], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FullName], [u].[Grade], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LastLoginAt], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[Role]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]

) AS [t]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Grade], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDataExported], [t].[StartDate], [t].[TimeSlot], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CourseId], [t0].[ProcessedAt], [t0].[RejectionReason], [t0].[RequestedAt], [t0].[Status], [t0].[StudentId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedAt], [t0].[Email], [t0].[FullName], [t0].[Grade], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[LastLoginAt], [t0].[PasswordHash], [t0].[Role]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[EndDate], [c].[Grade], [c].[IsActive], [c].[IsDataExported], [c].[StartDate], [c].[TimeSlot]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[Id] = @__courseId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CourseId], [c0].[ProcessedAt], [c0].[RejectionReason], [c0].[RequestedAt], [c0].[Status], [c0].[StudentId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FullName], [u].[Grade], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LastLoginAt], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[Role]
    FROM [CourseRegistrations] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [c0].[StudentId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CourseId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]

    WHERE [c].[Id] = [c0].[CourseId] AND [c0].[Status] = 2) AS [StudentCount], [c].[IsActive], CASE
    WHEN [c].[EndDate] <= @__now_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END AS [IsEnded], CASE
    WHEN [c].[EndDate] <= @__AddDays_1 AND [c].[EndDate] > @__now_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CourseId], [c0].[ProcessedAt], [c0].[RejectionReason], [c0].[RequestedAt], [c0].[Status], [c0].[StudentId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FullName], [u].[Grade], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LastLoginAt], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[Role]
    FROM [CourseRegistrations] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [c0].[StudentId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CourseId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]
